item.description:
@zyle1992 wrote:

[quote=“chri55w, post:2, topic:395269”]Client sided = wrong section,

however its in rsInterface.java

if(rsInterface.interfaceType == 4) { rsInterface.disabledMessage = stream.readString().replaceAll("RuneScape", "CruelalityX PK"); rsInterface.enabledMessage = stream.readString(); }

within the unpack void[/quote]

No.

Why does everyone suddenly think this is a client-side problem?

Look in your SERVER source files for “Luckscape”, every one of them, until you find it. Then replace it with your server’s name.
